{"tid":1450572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:55:51.000Z","uid":262042,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d42ec3dab9167f5e3dc0015ea72f12c5b4be686f","tid":1450572,"uid":262042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:43:22.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是我們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=9f255b3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=441eb670\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"5b0a90484cc51601a59f0a54cc7648404548be63","tid":1450572,"uid":103476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:45:46.000Z","msg":"致所有比狗打而想反抗嘅前線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1448193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1448193</a><br />\n<br />\n借位一用"},{"pid":"cefe424f7059575a62002a9ce88484a211ec0d2f","tid":1450572,"uid":9824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:46:08.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"acead0b40e055f3aa028b9d93fadbaf81d4bffa4","tid":1450572,"uid":114576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:55:51.000Z","msg":"［有文宣圖］「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1450